reviewText: First this double feature goes to Master Lee automatically; second in the last minutes of the Invincible it blanks out and goes to Master Lee. I purchased this because the better of the two movies ins Invincible kung Fu legs. Don't make the mistake I did and get this Double Feature movie. It's not worth $5.00 as the best fighting is at the end of the movie. Where the ground fighting style is fighting the King of the North (Leg kicks).
